HEADWORD: Higher National Diploma
<hw>Higher National Diploma</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Education)</fld>
<def>A certificate awarded for completing a course of vocational
education beyond secondary school, preparing the student for a career in
business or certain practical arts. It is a term used in the United
Kingdom.</def> <mark>[United Kingdom]</mark> ⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

